title: Jets Front Office Stunner; Dalton Scale
itunes:title: Jets Front Office Stunner; Dalton Scale
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal react to the news of the Jets firing General Manager Mike Maccagnan. The heroes then give their Dalton Scale rankings on where some major QBs fall on the famous scale. (26:34)
